Terrorsaur:




Terrorsaur kept a good altitude. He was actually enjoying this long range 
trip. He was cold, but that was all. He still had his air superiority. He 
was almost past the last marker that strange little Fuzor gave him. And 
after that, he would find Rowdy Wolf.

Knowing he said he would fire on him didn't make him feel safe, but he was 
quite a marksman himself. He was fast and skilled.

He had a feeling that he was being followed. He turned his head, seeing only 
a small dot on the ground. He used his scanners to find out who it was, and 
found out that it was only KitKat, one of the Predacons.

He opened his comm-link to her. "What are you doing out here? Did somebody 
send you?"
